   T. and Clark, Duncan B. and Pfefferbaum, Adolf and Pohl, Kilian M.},
Title = {{Influences of Age, Sex, and Moderate Alcohol Drinking on the Intrinsic
   Functional Architecture of Adolescent Brains}},
